PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food of BRENDA SCHOEPP of Rimbey, Alberta, to be a director of the Board of Directors of Farm Credit Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective February 10, 2013, in the place of Ron Hierath.
